d">Revolt Against the Modern World: Politics, Religion, and Social Order in the Kali Yuga</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Three_Aspects_of_the_Jewish_Problem" title="Three Aspects of the Jewish Problem">Three Aspects of the Jewish Problem</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/The_Mystery_of_the_Grail" title="The Mystery of the Grail">The Mystery of the Grail: Initiation and Magic in the Quest for the Spirit</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Il_Mito_del_Sangue._Genesi_del_Razzismo" title="Il Mito del Sangue. Genesi del Razzismo">Il Mito del Sangue. Genesi del Razzismo</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sintesi_di_Dottrina_della_Raza" title="Sintesi di Dottrina della Raza" class="mw-redirect">Sintesi di Dottrina della Raza</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/The_Elements_of_Racial_Education" title="The Elements of Racial Education">The Elements of Racial Education</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Die_Arische_Lehre_von_Kampf_und_Sieg" title="Die Arische Lehre von Kampf und Sieg">Die Arische Lehre von Kampf und Sieg</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Gli_Ebrei_hanno_volute_questa_Guerra" title="Gli Ebrei hanno volute questa Guerra" class="mw-redirect">Gli Ebrei hanno volute questa Guerra</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/The_Doctrine_of_Awakening" title="The Doctrine of Awakening">The Doctrine of Awakening: The Attainment of Self-Mastery According to the Earliest Buddhist Texts</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/The_Yoga_of_Power" title="The Yoga of Power">The Yoga of Power: Tantra, Shakti, and the Secret Way</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Orientamenti" title="Orientamenti">Orientamenti</a>&#160;|</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Men_Amo